content:
### Image Gallery

Build responsive image galleries with CSS.

---

### Grid Gallery

```css
.gallery {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 15px;
}

.gallery img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 250px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 8px;
}
```

---

### Masonry Gallery with Columns

```css
.masonry {
  columns: 3 250px;
  column-gap: 15px;
}

.masonry img {
  width: 100%;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  break-inside: avoid;
}
```

---

### Flexbox Gallery

```css
.flex-gallery {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
}

.flex-gallery img {
  flex: 1 1 200px;
  height: 200px;
  object-fit: cover;
}
```

---

### Gallery with Hover Overlay

```css
.gallery-item {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: 8px;
}

.gallery-item img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 250px;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.gallery-item:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.1);
}

.gallery-item .overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.3s;
  color: white;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.gallery-item:hover .overlay {
  opacity: 1;
}
```

---

### Aspect Ratio Gallery

```css
.gallery {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 10px;
}

.gallery img {
  width: 100%;
  aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 8px;
}

/* Featured image spans 2 columns */
.gallery img.featured {
  grid-column: span 2;
  grid-row: span 2;
}
```

---

> **Best Practice:** Use `object-fit: cover` for consistent image sizes. Use `aspect-ratio` for predictable dimensions.
